1
00:01:49,539 --> 00:01:54,940
[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:57,910
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,710
I know that

4
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,759
this method of weapon forging

5
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,870
involves your identity as a prince

6
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:01,740
and must not be leaked.

7
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:03,240
But she's a young lady after all,

8
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,570
and such a good one at that.

9
00:02:04,570 --> 00:02:05,650
Do you really expect me to torture her

10
00:02:05,650 --> 00:02:06,680
or silence her by killing?

11
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,230
What I meant is that...

12
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:07,870
No, don't talk yet.

13
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:08,639
Listen to me.

14
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:09,789
You know who Song Yiting is.

15
00:02:09,789 --> 00:02:11,330
Song Yiting is Song Yimeng's
younger sister.

16
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:12,630
If Song Yimeng's sister dies,

17
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:13,710
do you think she won't investigate?

18
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:15,310
And do you think she won't find out
it's you, Li Shiliu, behind it?

19
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:15,710
I...

20
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:17,470
So I think the top priority now

21
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,730
is to get the blade back

22
00:02:18,730 --> 00:02:20,130
instead of assigning blame.

23
00:02:20,130 --> 00:02:22,400
Tomorrow is the last day of the
three-day deadline.

24
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:25,930
Do you really have to get someone killed
at this critical point?

25
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,430
Are you done?

26
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:37,200
When did I ever say

27
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,510
I wanted to kill Song Yiting?

28
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,780
Or in your eyes,

29
00:02:41,810 --> 00:02:43,270
am I just someone who takes lives lightly,

30
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:44,220
commits all kinds of evil,

31
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,550
and is beyond redemption?

32
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:46,320
No, it's just

33
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:47,610
I've heard Song Yimeng say those things
about you

34
00:02:47,610 --> 00:02:48,430
so many times that I got influenced.

35
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,829
That's not what I meant.

36
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,000
Let me tell you,

37
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,050
I'll be blunt upfront.

38
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,410
If you get the blade back

39
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:57,740
and handle the aftermath properly,

40
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,540
we can put this matter behind us.

41
00:02:59,750 --> 00:03:01,610
But if you can't get the blade back

42
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:03,730
and cause me any more trouble,

43
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,410
I won't lay a hand on Song Yiting,

44
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:10,500
but I make no promises about
not dealing with you.

45
00:03:10,500 --> 00:03:11,500
Understand?

46
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,010
I understand.

47
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,240
You can get me out of jail,

48
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,770
and you can throw me back in.

49
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:16,870
Don't worry.

50
00:03:16,870 --> 00:03:18,100
I've already angered her today.

51
00:03:18,100 --> 00:03:19,910
I won't go see her tomorrow, either.

52
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,150
The moment the three-day deadline is up,

53
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:21,910
I'll go collect it immediately.

54
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:22,900
Why wait for three days?

55
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,780
Go tomorrow.

56
00:03:29,540 --> 00:03:30,510
Understood.

57
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:42,380
Wait, since when did you

58
00:03:42,730 --> 00:03:45,320
start caring so much about a woman?

59
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,220
I... I...

60
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,130
I...

61
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:52,060
You're not in love with her, are you?

62
00:03:52,670 --> 00:03:54,070
Of... Of course not.

63
00:03:58,660 --> 00:03:59,790
That's for the best.

64
00:04:01,890 --> 00:04:03,310
As your older brother,

65
00:04:03,780 --> 00:04:05,240
let me tell you something.

66
00:04:05,330 --> 00:04:07,000
This is the folly of love...

67
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:08,640
The weakness of heroes.

68
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:12,840
Good that you understand.

69
00:04:15,820 --> 00:04:17,300
But for a worthless man like me,

70
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,700
my spirit's even weaker.

71
00:04:36,659 --> 00:04:37,680
My Lady.

72
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:38,820
Please take a rest.

73
00:04:40,340 --> 00:04:42,470
No matter how many paintings you make,

74
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:45,240
you can't change Mr. Li's mind.

75
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,740
I'm not painting these

76
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:50,220
for him,

77
00:04:51,180 --> 00:04:52,930
but to remind myself

78
00:04:53,860 --> 00:04:55,150
how foolish I've been.

79
00:04:56,409 --> 00:04:58,870
I thought if I put my sincere heart
out there,

80
00:04:59,270 --> 00:05:01,470
it would definitely lead to something.

81
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:09,020
The way he saved me that day

82
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:12,060
keeps lingering in my mind.

83
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:14,910
Every time I think of it,

84
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,520
I make a painting.

85
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:20,160
73 paintings.

86
00:05:22,470 --> 00:05:23,500
I thought

87
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:26,570
I had truly fallen for him.

88
00:05:37,659 --> 00:05:38,470
My Lady!

89
00:05:39,659 --> 00:05:41,150
However many paintings I used
to think of him,

90
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:43,150
I'll need just as many to forget him.

91
00:05:43,180 --> 00:05:44,360
If one isn't enough,

92
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:45,880
then I'll tear up another!

93
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:47,630
My Lady!

94
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:48,630
My Lady!

95
00:05:48,909 --> 00:05:49,900
My Lady.

96
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,180
These...

97
00:05:51,290 --> 00:05:53,409
These are all your hard work!

98
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:54,950
Stop tearing them up.

99
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,390
Please stop.

100
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:59,340
He's just an ordinary man.

101
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:01,030
What makes him any different

102
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:02,400
from the others?

103
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:07,020
I, Song Yiting, will never be
trapped by love.

104
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,510
There are thousands of rivers
in this world,

105
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:11,310
so why settle for just one ladle?

106
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,430
[Seventh Prince's Mansion]

107
00:06:38,409 --> 00:06:40,670
He's had two bowls already this morning.

108
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:45,000
Good appetite suggests good mood.

109
00:06:46,020 --> 00:06:47,630
If he's in such a good mood,

110
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:49,530
could it be because of Yiting?

111
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:53,490
This dish is too salty.

112
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:56,630
Pickled vegetables are supposed
to be salty, okay?

113
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:58,159
Being so picky,

114
00:06:58,420 --> 00:07:01,920
could it be he had a fight with Yiting?

115
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:06,400
You're not eating?

116
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,220
Is it not to your taste?

117
00:07:09,590 --> 00:07:10,420
Or is it because

118
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:11,780
you fed me medicine yesterday,

119
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:14,440
you're expecting me to feed you
today in return?

120
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:16,630
I'd rather not,

121
00:07:16,660 --> 00:07:19,520
lest I soil Your Highness's clothes again.

122
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:27,710
You've been in the palace for 10 days now
since Mother brought you in.

123
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:29,390
Now that you've finally come out,

124
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,850
why not visit your family?

125
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:31,990
Don't you miss them?

126
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,170
Trying to get rid of me so soon,

127
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:38,909
can't wait to see Yiting, huh?

128
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:42,270
What's with that face?

129
00:07:44,180 --> 00:07:45,870
I was just wondering

130
00:07:46,230 --> 00:07:47,230
why Your Highness

131
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:49,600
suddenly started caring about my family.

132
00:07:51,340 --> 00:07:53,070
After we get married,

133
00:07:53,650 --> 00:07:54,650
your family

134
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:56,700
will be my family too, right?

135
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,140
I knew it,

136
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:03,630
you're up to something.

137
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:07,720
By the way,

138
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:10,340
does your sister have someone she likes?

139
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,450
I heard she's quite picky,

140
00:08:12,810 --> 00:08:14,720
and hasn't settled on an engagement yet.

141
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,380
What kind of man does she like?

142
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:20,740
You scumbag,

143
00:08:20,980 --> 00:08:22,640
already trying to make a move?

144
00:08:32,020 --> 00:08:33,419
Why did you slam the bowl?

145
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:35,289
What's wrong?

146
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,400
Well, Your Highness.

147
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:45,370
I-I suddenly have a stomachache.

148
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:47,530
You're having a stomachache?

149
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:49,510
I can't take it anymore.

150
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,990
My stomach hurts too much.

151
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:51,850
Your Highness.

152
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:53,750
Please enjoy your meal without me.

153
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:54,950
I'll head back first.

154
00:08:58,150 --> 00:09:00,480
Get an imperial physician to check on you.

155
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,230
Have you heard?

156
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:07,110
Song Yimeng has moved into the
Seventh Prince's Residence.

157
00:09:08,330 --> 00:09:09,870
They haven't even gotten married yet,

158
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,540
and she's already moved into
his residence.

159
00:09:11,540 --> 00:09:12,700
How inappropriate.

160
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,920
That one

161
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:15,420
always acts outrageously.

162
00:09:15,420 --> 00:09:17,680
When has she ever cared about propriety?

163
00:09:18,780 --> 00:09:20,010
I also heard that

164
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,150
she once went to a pharmacy

165
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:24,010
to buy that kind of medicine for
the Seventh Prince.

166
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:25,820
Really?

167
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:28,130
She really has no shame at all.

168
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,950
Yiting. Yiting.

169
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:31,710
You know the inside story best.

170
00:09:31,830 --> 00:09:32,830
Tell us,

171
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:34,350
how far have they gotten?

172
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,060
Yiting?

173
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:44,480
Yiting.

174
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:46,680
What's wrong?

175
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:48,880
You seem distracted.

176
00:09:49,450 --> 00:09:51,010
Are you in a bad mood?

177
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:56,140
You missed the gathering

178
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:57,450
the other day as well.

179
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:59,170
Did something happen?

180
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:02,030
Are you feeling unwell?

181
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:04,060
You're not sick, are you?

182
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:06,480
I know!

183
00:10:07,420 --> 00:10:08,700
Not seeing me for days

184
00:10:08,990 --> 00:10:10,350
has made her lovesick.

185
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:12,590
As for Miss Yiting's ailment,

186
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:13,390
I

187
00:10:12,740 --> 00:10:15,070
[Bamboo Mist, Rippling Moon]

188
00:10:13,580 --> 00:10:15,160
understand it best.

189
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:16,660
Your Highness.

190
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:18,520
Please, no need for formalities.

191
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,820
What brings you here, Your Highness?

192
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,210
I'm here

193
00:10:30,350 --> 00:10:32,670
to court you, Miss Yiting.

194
00:10:33,210 --> 00:10:34,010
Yiting.

195
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:36,900
His Highness is here for you.

196
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:37,690
Yiting.

197
00:10:38,130 --> 00:10:39,460
As for the question you asked me before,

198
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,770
I now have a new answer.

199
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:41,650
I've come today

200
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:43,250
to tell you in person.

201
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,730
Your Highness.

202
00:10:45,730 --> 00:10:47,060
What answer do you have?

203
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:49,470
I believe that

204
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:52,010
marriages should be based on
mutual affection

205
00:10:52,010 --> 00:10:53,060
and natural attraction.

206
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:55,010
Miss Yiting's talents and beauty

207
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,700
are merely external qualities.

208
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:58,220
What I truly love

209
00:10:58,820 --> 00:10:59,940
is your heart.

210
00:11:04,610 --> 00:11:06,210
Then tell me, Your Highness,

211
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:07,420
in your eyes,

212
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:09,940
what is my heart like?

213
00:11:11,610 --> 00:11:13,770
You refuse to be bound by
conventional etiquette

214
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:16,240
or commit yourself carelessly
to marriage.

215
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:18,300
You resent being controlled
by your parents,

216
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:20,940
and wish to escape what others call fate.

217
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:22,820
You reject others' advances

218
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:23,420
because you feel that

219
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,820
they only love your appearance,

220
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:26,770
and no one has ever asked

221
00:11:27,610 --> 00:11:28,940
who you really are.

222
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:31,800
But Yiting,

223
00:11:32,130 --> 00:11:33,660
I am different from others.

224
00:11:34,930 --> 00:11:36,530
The reason I like you

225
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:39,600
is simply because you are you.

226
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,610
If you love poetry and painting,

227
00:11:44,610 --> 00:11:45,750
I like you.

228
00:11:46,050 --> 00:11:47,530
If you love splendor and prosperity,

229
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:48,420
I like you.

230
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,730
Even if you're from

231
00:11:49,730 --> 00:11:50,370
every walk of life

232
00:11:50,370 --> 00:11:51,890
or a mere commoner,

233
00:11:52,890 --> 00:11:53,700
I still

234
00:11:54,650 --> 00:11:55,610
like you.

235
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:01,180
Yiting.

236
00:12:02,370 --> 00:12:03,580
I want to marry you.

237
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:07,180
From now on,

238
00:12:07,210 --> 00:12:08,670
I'll be the one to like you,

239
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:09,570
and you

240
00:12:10,890 --> 00:12:12,770
just need to be yourself.

241
00:12:16,850 --> 00:12:18,650
His Highness is...

242
00:12:19,340 --> 00:12:20,490
Proposing to you?

243
00:12:21,410 --> 00:12:22,280
Yiting,

244
00:12:22,730 --> 00:12:23,730
isn't this

245
00:12:23,730 --> 00:12:26,130
exactly what you've always wanted to hear?

246
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,100
Your Highness,

247
00:12:31,370 --> 00:12:32,530
please come with me.

248
00:12:47,010 --> 00:12:47,820
Tell me,

249
00:12:47,940 --> 00:12:49,300
who taught you to say that?

250
00:12:49,300 --> 00:12:50,180
No, I...

251
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:51,490
No, I...

252
00:12:52,350 --> 00:12:53,370
No one taught him.

253
00:12:53,730 --> 00:12:56,260
Those were all His Highness's
sincere words.

254
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:57,890
Yiting.

255
00:12:58,380 --> 00:13:00,250
I've liked you for so long after all,

256
00:13:00,250 --> 00:13:02,420
so I should've picked up some insights
by now, right?

257
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:03,010
Besides,

258
00:13:03,010 --> 00:13:05,130
today I was just overcome with emotion,

259
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:07,130
so I poured everything out at once.

260
00:13:07,130 --> 00:13:08,580
Seeing you doubt me like this,

261
00:13:08,580 --> 00:13:10,180
it kind of hurts my feelings.

262
00:13:10,180 --> 00:13:10,980
Really?

263
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:18,770
I'm sorry.

264
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:20,380
I was overthinking.

265
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:23,070
It's alright.

266
00:13:37,180 --> 00:13:37,940
Yiting! Yiting!

267
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:38,370
Don't. Don't!

268
00:13:38,370 --> 00:13:39,220
Wait, what are you doing?

269
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,020
Yiting, stop!

270
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,010
Wait, Yiting!

271
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:44,060
Yiting.

272
00:13:44,090 --> 00:13:46,540
Can I... Can I still explain myself?

273
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,490
Let go.

274
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:53,610
It's over, Jixiang.

275
00:14:01,730 --> 00:14:02,990
I'm done for, Jixiang.

276
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:06,010
It's all over.

277
00:14:11,100 --> 00:14:11,940
Liu Huaiyi.

278
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:13,400
What do you mean by that?

279
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:15,210
Am I wrong?

280
00:14:15,770 --> 00:14:16,900
Song Yiting

281
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:19,270
clearly wants to be the prince's consort.

282
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:21,320
But she has to play hard to get,

283
00:14:21,820 --> 00:14:24,820
making the Eighteenth Prince
beg for her attention.

284
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:27,250
When it comes to playing hard to get
the way she does,

285
00:14:27,250 --> 00:14:29,280
no one else can compare.

286
00:14:29,610 --> 00:14:31,250
Yiting is not that kind of person.

287
00:14:31,250 --> 00:14:32,980
That's because she's good at pretending,

288
00:14:32,980 --> 00:14:35,300
acting all innocent and unworldly.

289
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:38,490
But among all the unmarried ladies
in the capital,

290
00:14:38,490 --> 00:14:39,670
she's the one

291
00:14:40,010 --> 00:14:42,700
who knows best how to catch
men's attention.

292
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:45,940
Why else would the Eighteenth Prince
notice her?

293
00:14:46,130 --> 00:14:47,170
Liu Huaiyi.

294
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:48,700
Talking behind her back,

295
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,060
what kind of friend are you?

296
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:51,170
Alright, alright.

297
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:52,530
Stop arguing.

298
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:55,100
We've been friends for so many years.

299
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:56,940
It's not worth ruining our friendship

300
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:57,940
over something so trivial.

301
00:14:57,940 --> 00:14:59,940
We may consider Song Yiting our friend,

302
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:01,770
but she might not feel the same way.

303
00:15:01,770 --> 00:15:02,940
All these years,

304
00:15:03,010 --> 00:15:04,840
she's been looking down on us.

305
00:15:04,940 --> 00:15:07,230
Has she ever truly respected any of us?

306
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:08,560
I'll tear your mouth apart!

307
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:09,080
You...

308
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:09,700
Alright, calm down, Ruru.

309
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:10,610
You're angry at me?

310
00:15:10,610 --> 00:15:12,530
You're the most pathetic one, Jia Ruru,

311
00:15:12,530 --> 00:15:14,530
following Song Yiting around all day

312
00:15:14,530 --> 00:15:15,770
like some echo,

313
00:15:15,770 --> 00:15:17,220
yet understanding nothing.

314
00:15:17,220 --> 00:15:18,300
This whole scene today

315
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:20,900
was clearly planned by Song Yiting
in advance!

316
00:15:25,010 --> 00:15:26,870
All sweet and sisterly in public,

317
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:28,750
but backstabbing in private.

318
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:30,200
Miss Liu, you truly

319
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:32,700
live up to your reputation as
a noble lady.

320
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:34,370
Who is it?

321
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,490
This is between us friends.

322
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:37,940
Who are you to lecture me?

323
00:15:38,490 --> 00:15:39,700
Matters between friends

324
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:41,980
are indeed not my place to comment on.

325
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:43,420
However, I believe

326
00:15:43,610 --> 00:15:44,850
that in relationships,

327
00:15:44,850 --> 00:15:46,450
sincerity is most valuable.

328
00:15:46,850 --> 00:15:48,580
She prepared new clothes and new jewelry

329
00:15:48,580 --> 00:15:50,670
just for today's gathering.

330
00:15:50,770 --> 00:15:51,990
Even if you cannot repay this friendship

331
00:15:51,990 --> 00:15:54,210
in kind, you shouldn't treat

332
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:56,700
sincere feelings like they're worthless.

333
00:15:58,260 --> 00:15:59,940
Now I get it.

334
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,970
Just another one defending her.

335
00:16:02,060 --> 00:16:03,340
One's a prince,

336
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:06,320
the other's a charlatan like you.

337
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:08,320
Song Yiting really is something.

338
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:10,650
There's no man she can't seduce.

339
00:16:18,730 --> 00:16:19,660
Are you alright?

340
00:16:20,530 --> 00:16:21,920
Who exactly are you?

341
00:16:22,650 --> 00:16:26,010
Just a stranger who couldn't stand by
and watch injustice.

342
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:26,890
You...

343
00:16:26,890 --> 00:16:27,730
Well done!

344
00:16:27,730 --> 00:16:28,340
Beautifully done!

345
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:29,690
Good job!

346
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:31,060
Mister.

347
00:16:31,130 --> 00:16:32,490
Would you like to come in for some tea

348
00:16:32,490 --> 00:16:33,670
and rest for a while?

349
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:01,980
Why did you come anyway, Mr. Li?

350
00:17:05,859 --> 00:17:06,940
Just passing by.

351
00:17:08,940 --> 00:17:11,170
Out of the entire wide capital,

352
00:17:11,290 --> 00:17:13,089
you just so happened to "pass by"
right here?

353
00:17:13,089 --> 00:17:14,619
If you were just passing by,

354
00:17:14,730 --> 00:17:15,900
why did you bother

355
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,900
getting involved and defending me?

356
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:19,569
After all, we've known each other
for some time,

357
00:17:19,569 --> 00:17:21,290
so it's only right that I
defend you a bit.

358
00:17:21,290 --> 00:17:22,900
Besides, it's really unfair of them

359
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:25,010
to say such things about you
behind your back.

360
00:17:25,010 --> 00:17:27,410
I was talking about the Eighteenth Prince.

361
00:17:30,660 --> 00:17:32,770
Those things the Eighteenth Prince said,

362
00:17:32,770 --> 00:17:34,900
you taught him to say them, didn't you?

363
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:39,780
You clearly know me well,

364
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:41,460
yet you deliberately anger me

365
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,650
and push me away.

366
00:17:42,770 --> 00:17:43,730
Why?

367
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:47,450
Knowing you and liking you

368
00:17:47,570 --> 00:17:48,970
are two separate things.

369
00:17:49,530 --> 00:17:51,350
You're the most special

370
00:17:51,490 --> 00:17:53,100
and wonderful girl I've ever met.

371
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:54,570
Even if I don't have feelings for you,

372
00:17:54,570 --> 00:17:56,060
you still deserve to be appreciated

373
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:57,050
and treated well.

374
00:17:57,050 --> 00:17:57,940
You're lying.

375
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:00,280
You just said

376
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:01,460
that in relationships,

377
00:18:01,460 --> 00:18:02,980
sincerity is most valuable.

378
00:18:02,980 --> 00:18:03,980
Then, Li Shiliu,

379
00:18:04,010 --> 00:18:05,530
please honestly tell me,

380
00:18:06,290 --> 00:18:09,050
have you ever had feelings for me?

381
00:18:12,810 --> 00:18:14,560
If even half a word is a lie,

382
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:15,660
may heaven strike you down.

383
00:18:15,660 --> 00:18:16,380
I,

384
00:18:21,090 --> 00:18:22,240
Li Shiliu,

385
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:24,700
have never had feelings for you.

386
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:26,790
Say it again.

387
00:18:26,810 --> 00:18:28,900
No matter how many times I say it,
it won't change.

388
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:29,930
Li Shiliu

389
00:18:30,050 --> 00:18:31,220
has never had feelings for you.

390
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:33,380
So you pushed me toward the
Eighteenth Prince,

391
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:35,180
taking advantage of when you discarded me

392
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:36,760
to let him approach me?

393
00:18:37,700 --> 00:18:38,980
You've misjudged me.

394
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:42,150
I, Song Yiting, am not someone
who can't accept defeat.

395
00:18:42,490 --> 00:18:44,380
I just felt that I hurt you,

396
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:45,940
and if there could be someone who
truly cared for you

397
00:18:45,940 --> 00:18:46,700
by your side,

398
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:47,660
you might feel better.

399
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:49,140
Stop deceiving yourself.

400
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:51,950
You just wanted to make yourself
feel better.

401
00:18:52,330 --> 00:18:54,090
In your eyes, I'm nothing more than

402
00:18:54,090 --> 00:18:55,690
a piece of clothing

403
00:18:55,810 --> 00:18:57,010
or a piece of jewelry.

404
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,350
But even if you don't like me,

405
00:18:59,460 --> 00:19:02,010
what right do you have to push me
onto someone else?

406
00:19:02,010 --> 00:19:03,770
I never thought of you that way.

407
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:04,980
Li Shiliu.

408
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,390
You love to lecture others,

409
00:19:07,700 --> 00:19:08,990
but you're not worthy.

410
00:19:09,860 --> 00:19:11,170
You teach others that

411
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:12,460
marriages are about mutual affection and

412
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,660
natural attraction,

413
00:19:14,490 --> 00:19:17,490
but you yourself don't understand
what love is at all.

414
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:19,660
You tell others

415
00:19:20,140 --> 00:19:21,940
not to disregard true feelings,

416
00:19:22,660 --> 00:19:24,420
yet you have no heart at all.

417
00:19:27,290 --> 00:19:28,730
I used to like you

418
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:32,370
because I thought you were different
from others.

419
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:33,530
But from now on,

420
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,750
I won't like you anymore,

421
00:19:37,140 --> 00:19:38,570
because I despise you

422
00:19:39,420 --> 00:19:40,950
even more than anyone else.

423
00:19:44,770 --> 00:19:45,570
I'm sorry.

424
00:19:48,250 --> 00:19:49,050
Don't bother.

425
00:19:50,250 --> 00:19:51,480
Tomorrow at noon,

426
00:19:51,730 --> 00:19:53,730
at Zijin Pavilion outside the city,

427
00:19:54,090 --> 00:19:55,820
I'll return what you asked for.

428
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:57,630
Please kindly

429
00:19:58,060 --> 00:20:00,060
bring back my paintings too, Mr. Li.

430
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:02,120
Don't soil my belongings.

431
00:20:11,570 --> 00:20:12,630
She... He... He...

432
00:20:12,630 --> 00:20:13,650
They...

433
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:16,370
They're a real couple?

434
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,740
What about me?

435
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:20,350
What am I to her?

436
00:20:22,020 --> 00:20:23,810
Probably just a laughingstock
who copied Mr. Li's love lines

437
00:20:23,810 --> 00:20:25,540
yet failed in your confession.

438
00:20:26,380 --> 00:20:27,490
Nonsense!

439
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:28,770
It must be that Li Shiliu.

440
00:20:28,770 --> 00:20:30,440
He... He must have deliberately
played me,

441
00:20:30,440 --> 00:20:31,850
making me look foolish in front of Yiting

442
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:33,580
and paving the way for himself.

443
00:20:34,010 --> 00:20:35,570
I'm the auspicious sign of the Great Jing.

444
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:37,500
How could I be treated so unjustly?

445
00:20:38,310 --> 00:20:39,270
Just you wait.

446
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:40,780
I must prove to Yiting

447
00:20:40,800 --> 00:20:41,500
that Li Shiliu,

448
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:43,760
he... He's not such a good person either.

449
00:20:46,180 --> 00:20:46,980
Either?

450
00:20:49,070 --> 00:20:50,140
Did I say "either"?

451
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:53,060
[Gentle Breeze]

452
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,520
Father?

453
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:08,280
[Song Residence]

454
00:21:27,630 --> 00:21:28,510
Madam...

455
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:35,400
You'd better explain to me

456
00:21:35,530 --> 00:21:37,180
what this is about.

457
00:21:37,820 --> 00:21:39,150
Whose portrait is this?

458
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:42,830
What do you mean by that?

459
00:21:43,010 --> 00:21:44,670
What happened to Song Yiting?

460
00:21:45,330 --> 00:21:46,370
Yimeng,

461
00:21:47,490 --> 00:21:48,750
there are some matters

462
00:21:49,330 --> 00:21:51,620
I shouldn't have troubled you with,

463
00:21:51,770 --> 00:21:53,570
but I don't know what's gotten
into Yiting lately.

464
00:21:53,570 --> 00:21:55,380
Maybe it's because she's fallen
for someone,

465
00:21:55,380 --> 00:21:56,460
she wouldn't listen to her mother

466
00:21:56,460 --> 00:21:58,660
about marrying the Eighteenth Prince,

467
00:21:59,010 --> 00:22:01,590
and the whole family is in chaos
because of this.

468
00:22:01,590 --> 00:22:02,620
Oh no.

469
00:22:03,570 --> 00:22:05,700
She's already fallen in love with him.

470
00:22:07,530 --> 00:22:08,730
Father, don't worry.

471
00:22:09,110 --> 00:22:10,240
I'll see this matter

472
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:11,900
through to the end.

473
00:22:15,330 --> 00:22:16,140
Chief.

474
00:22:16,490 --> 00:22:17,630
Miss Song is here.

475
00:22:21,420 --> 00:22:23,160
What brings you here today?

476
00:22:25,170 --> 00:22:25,960
Mr. Li.

477
00:22:25,980 --> 00:22:27,980
You really need to help me this time.

478
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:29,450
Please.

479
00:22:33,300 --> 00:22:34,450
Spit it out!

480
00:22:35,180 --> 00:22:36,670
Who exactly is that man?

481
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:37,860
I...

482
00:22:37,980 --> 00:22:40,750
I really don't know.

483
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:42,560
Fine.

484
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:44,400
If she refuses to talk,

485
00:22:44,490 --> 00:22:45,460
I won't keep

486
00:22:45,620 --> 00:22:46,810
this wretched life of hers!

487
00:22:46,810 --> 00:22:47,620
Beat her!

488
00:22:51,980 --> 00:22:52,980
Stop beating her!

489
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:55,320
Stop it!

490
00:22:55,350 --> 00:22:56,390
My Lady.

491
00:22:57,150 --> 00:22:58,310
Stop this at once!

492
00:23:02,570 --> 00:23:03,330
Mother!

493
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:04,490
What are you doing?

494
00:23:05,490 --> 00:23:06,960
You're asking me?

495
00:23:07,180 --> 00:23:09,440
I should be asking you what you're doing!

496
00:23:09,770 --> 00:23:10,900
I heard from the doorman

497
00:23:10,900 --> 00:23:12,010
that you've been calling for carriages
every day

498
00:23:12,010 --> 00:23:14,080
just to meet a man in secret!

499
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:15,250
Did I raise you

500
00:23:15,280 --> 00:23:16,860
just so you could degrade yourself

501
00:23:16,860 --> 00:23:18,750
by associating with some scum?

502
00:23:19,460 --> 00:23:21,330
My relationship with him is proper
and respectful.

503
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:23,380
And he's not some scum you make
him out to be!

504
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:24,780
Proper relationship?

505
00:23:26,090 --> 00:23:27,140
How dare you say

506
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:28,860
something so improper!

507
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:30,640
Are you trying to anger me to death?

508
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:32,640
So what do you call proper behavior?

509
00:23:32,770 --> 00:23:34,090
Dressing myself up

510
00:23:34,090 --> 00:23:35,530
to parade before sons of noble families,

511
00:23:35,530 --> 00:23:36,620
is that proper behavior?

512
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:38,330
If it were the Eighteenth Prince today,

513
00:23:38,330 --> 00:23:39,490
forget about secret meetings,

514
00:23:39,490 --> 00:23:40,900
even if I had an improper affair with him,

515
00:23:40,900 --> 00:23:42,570
you'd still thank our ancestors
for the blessing

516
00:23:42,570 --> 00:23:45,170
and wish everyone in the capital
knew about it!

517
00:23:47,420 --> 00:23:49,290
Are you trying to anger me to death?

518
00:23:49,290 --> 00:23:50,420
You should know that

519
00:23:50,530 --> 00:23:52,940
if this ever gets out,

520
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:54,120
your reputation

521
00:23:54,220 --> 00:23:55,750
will be completely ruined!

522
00:23:57,900 --> 00:23:59,560
Reputation is like a shackle,

523
00:23:59,700 --> 00:24:02,630
which deserves to be discarded
like tattered shoes.

524
00:24:03,250 --> 00:24:04,270
Shannai,

525
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:05,180
let's go.

526
00:24:08,220 --> 00:24:08,980
Impossible.

527
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:10,220
That's impossible.

528
00:24:11,490 --> 00:24:12,590
I know

529
00:24:12,770 --> 00:24:14,980
it sounds ridiculous.

530
00:24:15,090 --> 00:24:15,810
But last time

531
00:24:15,810 --> 00:24:17,090
when I predicted the fire,

532
00:24:17,090 --> 00:24:18,380
didn't it happen as I said?

533
00:24:18,380 --> 00:24:21,640
Right now, Nan Heng is really
planning to kill Song Yiting.

534
00:24:22,290 --> 00:24:23,290
Mr. Li.

535
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:24,610
I really need you to help me.

536
00:24:24,610 --> 00:24:26,610
Otherwise, Yiting will be done for.

537
00:24:26,940 --> 00:24:28,730
Everything needs evidence.

538
00:24:29,860 --> 00:24:30,860
As far as I know,

539
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:34,210
between Nan Heng and Song Yiting,
there's absolutely no...

540
00:24:38,460 --> 00:24:39,250
Anyway,

541
00:24:40,050 --> 00:24:41,910
this must be a misunderstanding.

542
00:24:43,090 --> 00:24:44,300
How could it be?

543
00:24:44,320 --> 00:24:45,720
When it comes to romance,

544
00:24:45,750 --> 00:24:47,060
do you think you know
more than I do?

545
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:47,700
I...

546
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:51,620
Mr. Li.

547
00:24:51,660 --> 00:24:53,330
Let's not argue about this right now,

548
00:24:53,330 --> 00:24:53,940
okay?

549
00:24:53,940 --> 00:24:55,140
I can tell at a glance

550
00:24:55,140 --> 00:24:56,160
if a man has ulterior motives

551
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:57,440
toward a woman.

552
00:24:57,510 --> 00:24:58,860
For example, from the way Nan Heng
looks at Yiting,

553
00:24:58,860 --> 00:25:00,280
it's obvious he's up to no good.

554
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:01,340
But the way you look at me

555
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:03,100
is merely friendly, Mr. Li.

556
00:25:08,380 --> 00:25:09,180
You...

557
00:25:10,290 --> 00:25:11,090
You...

558
00:25:12,460 --> 00:25:14,290
What are you doing?

559
00:25:16,190 --> 00:25:18,350
Do you believe that I like women now?

560
00:25:20,330 --> 00:25:21,530
So,

561
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:23,730
you were

562
00:25:24,050 --> 00:25:25,250
kissing me just now?

563
00:25:27,490 --> 00:25:29,020
You still don't believe me?

