00:26:16,570 --> 00:26:17,630
So, I don't want

570
00:26:17,940 --> 00:26:19,270
to hear any more of that talk

571
00:26:19,270 --> 00:26:21,530
about us being friends
from you anymore.

572
00:26:22,770 --> 00:26:23,800
Didn't you say

573
00:26:24,090 --> 00:26:26,350
you understand romance better than I do?

574
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:28,420
Then tell me,

575
00:26:28,460 --> 00:26:29,620
what does this

576
00:26:30,330 --> 00:26:31,140
make us?

577
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,730
Well...

578
00:26:40,730 --> 00:26:41,780
I think...

579
00:26:56,980 --> 00:26:58,510
What we have between us isn't friendship.

580
00:26:58,510 --> 00:27:00,270
It's not friendship.

581
00:27:03,380 --> 00:27:04,270
But who

582
00:27:05,030 --> 00:27:07,350
kisses with a mask on?

583
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:12,770
Chief really went for it.

584
00:27:12,940 --> 00:27:14,500
He actually kissed her.

585
00:27:14,570 --> 00:27:17,300
Let's see if he dares to kiss her
without the mask.

586
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:37,700
What's wrong?

587
00:27:38,420 --> 00:27:40,080
Drowning your sorrows alone?

588
00:27:43,660 --> 00:27:44,900
Shanhu has filled me in

589
00:27:44,900 --> 00:27:47,300
on what's been going on
these past few days.

590
00:27:48,570 --> 00:27:49,380
What?

591
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:52,640
You want to blame me for
messing things up again?

592
00:27:53,460 --> 00:27:54,250
Go ahead.

593
00:27:58,660 --> 00:27:59,590
You fell in love?

594
00:28:09,570 --> 00:28:11,410
Just days ago, I was teasing you

595
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:14,810
about how Song Yimeng had you
completely smitten.

596
00:28:15,560 --> 00:28:17,360
Look how the tables have turned.

597
00:28:17,770 --> 00:28:19,170
It's only been a few days,

598
00:28:19,810 --> 00:28:21,460
and now you're the audience,

599
00:28:21,610 --> 00:28:22,640
while I've become

600
00:28:23,290 --> 00:28:24,460
the performer.

601
00:28:26,490 --> 00:28:27,740
Your little drama

602
00:28:27,770 --> 00:28:29,970
isn't worth my time and effort to watch.

603
00:28:31,530 --> 00:28:32,620
But the question is,

604
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:34,010
if you like her,

605
00:28:34,040 --> 00:28:35,390
why don't you go win her back?

606
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:36,650
Why sit here brooding?

607
00:28:37,470 --> 00:28:38,380
And then what?

608
00:28:38,950 --> 00:28:40,810
Live happily ever after with her?

609
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:43,090
Or one day when my identity is exposed,

610
00:28:43,090 --> 00:28:44,400
I'll drag the entire Waning River Crescent

611
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:46,160
and her into this mess?

612
00:28:47,620 --> 00:28:49,790
Don't overestimate yourself, okay?

613
00:28:49,810 --> 00:28:52,610
As if my Waning River Crescent
needs your concern.

614
00:28:55,980 --> 00:28:56,780
You're right.

615
00:28:57,900 --> 00:29:00,300
I have no right to think so
highly of myself.

616
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,060
I haven't forgotten that

617
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,590
you and I

618
00:29:03,930 --> 00:29:05,800
are also just part of a deal.

619
00:29:08,670 --> 00:29:09,470
That's true.

620
00:29:15,330 --> 00:29:17,590
Do you remember who I was three years ago?

621
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:22,910
Three years ago,

622
00:29:24,010 --> 00:29:26,940
you were a famous hero in Jiangnan,
Shangguan Baihe,

623
00:29:26,950 --> 00:29:28,880
known as Mr. Shangguan.

624
00:29:29,400 --> 00:29:30,380
Within half a month,

625
00:29:30,380 --> 00:29:32,710
you committed more than 10 major thefts.

626
00:29:32,900 --> 00:29:35,100
I led 2,000 Xuanjia Army soldiers,

627
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:37,740
mobilizing forces from three provinces
and six cities,

628
00:29:37,740 --> 00:29:39,400
yet still failed to catch you.

629
00:29:40,490 --> 00:29:41,330
But later,

630
00:29:41,330 --> 00:29:42,980
you were exposed because

631
00:29:43,180 --> 00:29:44,700
a friend betrayed you.

632
00:29:46,860 --> 00:29:49,090
Back then, I, Baihe, trusted
the wrong person

633
00:29:49,090 --> 00:29:50,330
and fell into a trap,

634
00:29:50,950 --> 00:29:52,230
with no way out.

635
00:29:52,860 --> 00:29:54,470
In the end, I had no choice but to

636
00:29:54,470 --> 00:29:55,950
break my wings to survive.

637
00:30:00,630 --> 00:30:01,910
Are you blaming me,

638
00:30:02,570 --> 00:30:04,090
for clipping your wings

639
00:30:04,340 --> 00:30:07,380
and trapping you in this small
Waning River Crescent?

640
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:09,810
Yes.

641
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:13,210
I hate you, the mighty Seventh Prince,
to the core

642
00:30:13,210 --> 00:30:14,770
for not letting me die.

643
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:21,120
[Three years ago]

644
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:22,400
The Ministry of Justice has issued
their verdict.

645
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:25,060
You've been sentenced to
immediate execution,

646
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,480
which will be carried out tomorrow.

647
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:30,800
It's been seven days.

648
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:32,790
You come every single day.

649
00:30:33,980 --> 00:30:36,740
Could you give a dying man
one day of peace?

650
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:40,160
If I were you,

651
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:43,090
I'd try my best to find a way
out of here alive

652
00:30:43,500 --> 00:30:45,180
to see what color blood runs in someone

653
00:30:45,180 --> 00:30:47,340
who would betray their companion

654
00:30:47,700 --> 00:30:49,030
for 2,000 taels of gold.

655
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:56,960
The person you speak of
who betrayed their companion

656
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,010
is both an enemy

657
00:30:58,900 --> 00:31:00,200
and a friend to me.

658
00:31:02,010 --> 00:31:03,720
Your enemy framed you,

659
00:31:04,110 --> 00:31:04,920
betrayed you,

660
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:06,660
and kept all the riches for himself,

661
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:08,750
yet you still consider him a friend.

662
00:31:09,050 --> 00:31:10,780
It seems you deserve your fate.

663
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,240
Someone like you,

664
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:17,450
born into privilege,

665
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:21,250
could never understand what kind of life

666
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:24,770
he and I lived before.

667
00:31:25,810 --> 00:31:27,140
Wrapped in horsehide upon death,

668
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,940
licking blood from blade edges,

669
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,940
and entrusting your back to comrades.

670
00:31:30,940 --> 00:31:33,140
This prince believes the past you speak of

671
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:34,930
wasn't much harder than this.

672
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,040
"This prince"?

673
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,620
Who are you?

674
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:41,010
Who I am doesn't matter.

675
00:31:41,580 --> 00:31:42,550
What matters is

676
00:31:42,730 --> 00:31:43,860
you're still alive.

677
00:31:44,330 --> 00:31:45,660
As long as we're alive,

678
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:48,790
we should cherish every single day.

679
00:31:48,860 --> 00:31:50,580
Friends gone? So be it.

680
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:52,660
Path blocked? Carve through mountains.

681
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:54,470
But if your life is gone,

682
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:57,270
that's truly the end.

683
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:11,450
Here's to shady friends.

684
00:32:13,190 --> 00:32:13,910
Alright.

685
00:32:13,930 --> 00:32:15,530
To disreputable companion.

686
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,600
Heart like wood and stone,

687
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,460
utterly cold and unfeeling.

688
00:32:26,860 --> 00:32:28,860
You're not speaking from the heart.

689
00:32:29,740 --> 00:32:30,820
However, I never expected

690
00:32:30,820 --> 00:32:32,490
you'd be troubled by love.

691
00:32:32,520 --> 00:32:34,430
Like master, like man.

692
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:35,960
When it comes to being troubled by love,

693
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,960
you, Chief, are the true expert.

694
00:32:38,180 --> 00:32:40,110
I can't hold a candle to you on that.

695
00:32:42,620 --> 00:32:43,910
But the point is,

696
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,420
I never pushed the person I love

697
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:46,880
into someone else's arms.

698
00:32:47,090 --> 00:32:47,920
Besides,

699
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:50,120
the lady doesn't even like Nan Rui,

700
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:52,270
yet you think you're doing her a favor.

701
00:32:56,220 --> 00:32:57,700
That blabbermouth Shanhu,

702
00:32:57,700 --> 00:32:59,060
telling everything.

703
00:33:00,330 --> 00:33:01,940
What does this have to do with Shanhu?

704
00:33:01,940 --> 00:33:03,740
You have only yourself to blame.

705
00:33:03,770 --> 00:33:06,380
You not only messed it up,

706
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:08,380
but you also broke the lady's heart.

707
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:19,890
I was a prisoner

708
00:33:20,050 --> 00:33:21,940
who should have died long ago.

709
00:33:23,330 --> 00:33:26,490
There's no way I could fall in love with
a lady from a noble family.

710
00:33:26,490 --> 00:33:27,560
Chief,

711
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:29,980
don't you understand?

712
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:32,960
It doesn't matter whether I understand.

713
00:33:32,970 --> 00:33:34,210
What matters is,

714
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,920
does Song Yiting understand?

715
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,630
Whether she understands or not
doesn't matter,

716
00:33:37,630 --> 00:33:39,810
because the person she likes
isn't the real me.

717
00:33:39,810 --> 00:33:41,110
Then tell her

718
00:33:41,130 --> 00:33:43,460
what you're really like beneath the mask.

719
00:33:43,490 --> 00:33:44,750
So, if Song Yimeng knew

720
00:33:44,760 --> 00:33:46,380
what you're really like beneath that mask,

721
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,440
how would she feel?

722
00:33:47,620 --> 00:33:48,070
I...

723
00:33:51,330 --> 00:33:52,010
See?

724
00:33:57,940 --> 00:33:59,380
This Li Shiliu's outfit

725
00:33:59,910 --> 00:34:02,170
has really caused quite a bit of trouble.

726
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:04,130
All the frustration in your heart

727
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:06,040
stems from Song Yiting.

728
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:08,199
Why not just ask her out

729
00:34:08,460 --> 00:34:09,540
and tell her

730
00:34:09,560 --> 00:34:11,170
everything that's on your mind?

731
00:34:11,170 --> 00:34:11,940
This way,

732
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:14,409
you won't have any regrets in the future.

733
00:34:19,989 --> 00:34:21,389
What if I don't want to go?

734
00:34:24,380 --> 00:34:25,550
If you don't go,

735
00:34:26,340 --> 00:34:27,949
then the crane in your heart

736
00:34:27,969 --> 00:34:29,790
will remain trapped in your mental prison,

737
00:34:29,790 --> 00:34:32,389
and you'll be left with nothing
but your title.

738
00:34:45,340 --> 00:34:46,460
Tomorrow at noon,

739
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:48,130
let me borrow

740
00:34:48,590 --> 00:34:50,449
Li Shiliu's outfit one more time.

741
00:34:51,730 --> 00:34:52,920
That's more like it.

742
00:34:54,050 --> 00:34:54,860
Here.

743
00:34:55,420 --> 00:34:56,480
Tomorrow,

744
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:58,670
bring both the Qianyu Moon-Cleaving Blade

745
00:34:58,670 --> 00:35:00,170
and yourself with your heart intact

746
00:35:00,170 --> 00:35:01,650
back to me.

747
00:35:01,780 --> 00:35:02,640
Understand?

748
00:35:05,300 --> 00:35:06,090
Come on.

749
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:08,590
Success awaits you.

750
00:35:09,540 --> 00:35:12,600
[Xiyue Pavilion]

751
00:35:11,900 --> 00:35:12,690
My Lady.

752
00:35:13,090 --> 00:35:14,090
I'm sorry.

753
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:17,250
It's all my fault for being careless

754
00:35:17,250 --> 00:35:19,020
and letting Madam find out.

755
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:22,610
It doesn't matter anymore.

756
00:35:23,370 --> 00:35:26,410
He wouldn't be with me anyway.

757
00:35:28,510 --> 00:35:30,440
He'd rather push me to someone else

758
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:32,490
than admit he has feelings for me.

759
00:35:33,260 --> 00:35:34,300
In his eyes,

760
00:35:34,750 --> 00:35:35,830
I'm nothing.

761
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:38,740
If you see it so clearly,

762
00:35:38,770 --> 00:35:40,770
why do you still have to love him?

763
00:35:43,690 --> 00:35:45,410
I know exactly what I'm doing.

764
00:35:45,490 --> 00:35:47,490
I don't need others preaching to me.

765
00:35:48,380 --> 00:35:50,980
If you're here as our parents' messenger,

766
00:35:50,980 --> 00:35:51,900
please leave.

767
00:35:53,610 --> 00:35:54,460
Song Yiting,

768
00:35:55,050 --> 00:35:57,050
you've always been so strong-willed.

769
00:35:57,050 --> 00:35:59,380
Why would you fall for someone like him?

770
00:35:59,570 --> 00:36:01,340
Don't you know what kind of person he is?

771
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,460
Deep and calculating,

772
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:03,770
and secretive in his actions.

773
00:36:03,770 --> 00:36:05,780
Do you know how many dirty secrets

774
00:36:05,780 --> 00:36:06,650
he's hiding?

775
00:36:09,300 --> 00:36:10,490
Yes, he's deep and calculating,

776
00:36:10,490 --> 00:36:11,940
and secretive in his actions,

777
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,380
but if he hadn't experienced

778
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:14,740
all the hardships of life in his
early years

779
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:15,900
and struggled to survive,

780
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:17,230
why would he be this way?

781
00:36:19,490 --> 00:36:20,300
Fine.

782
00:36:20,740 --> 00:36:22,070
You can ignore all that,

783
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,130
but do you know he's approaching you

784
00:36:24,130 --> 00:36:25,630
with ulterior motives?

785
00:36:26,380 --> 00:36:27,460
Of course I know.

786
00:36:28,170 --> 00:36:30,210
If it weren't for what he wants,

787
00:36:30,380 --> 00:36:32,470
he wouldn't agree to meet me.

788
00:36:32,690 --> 00:36:33,630
You know all this

789
00:36:33,660 --> 00:36:35,860
and still let him take advantage of you?

790
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:38,980
A blade in hand

791
00:36:39,090 --> 00:36:40,170
can either kill

792
00:36:40,490 --> 00:36:41,570
or save the world.

793
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,540
I trust my judgment.

794
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:46,210
I won't be wrong about him.

795
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,420
What're you talking about,
saving the world?

796
00:36:48,420 --> 00:36:50,040
Don't be fooled by his twisted logic

797
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,050
and false words.

798
00:36:51,050 --> 00:36:52,390
Beneath his mask,

799
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:54,500
he's nothing but a complete villain.

800
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:57,070
But who's not wearing a mask
in this world?

801
00:36:57,860 --> 00:36:59,070
In the capital,

802
00:36:59,340 --> 00:37:00,570
who's not scheming

803
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,260
and chasing fame and fortune?

804
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:03,420
And who

805
00:37:03,420 --> 00:37:04,620
would ever show

806
00:37:04,650 --> 00:37:06,140
their true self to others?

807
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:08,820
It's actually him

808
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:11,260
who lives freely and authentically,

809
00:37:11,260 --> 00:37:12,630
without restraint.

810
00:37:16,690 --> 00:37:18,550
I really can't get through to you.

811
00:37:18,940 --> 00:37:20,060
Please, I'm begging you,

812
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:20,930
alright?

813
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:22,690
Don't get involved with him.

814
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,170
In this world,

815
00:37:25,340 --> 00:37:27,170
you can fall for anyone,

816
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,750
anyone but him.

817
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:31,820
Why not him?

818
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:33,850
Just because he's not
the Eighteenth Prince,

819
00:37:33,850 --> 00:37:35,580
he doesn't deserve to be loved?

820
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,630
That's not what I meant.

821
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:39,460
Then why are you trying to dissuade me?

822
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:40,800
And what gives you the right

823
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:42,130
to interfere in my life?

824
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,370
Song Yiting.

825
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:50,320
I really don't know

826
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:54,050
how to explain this to you.

827
00:37:54,490 --> 00:37:55,980
But please believe me,

828
00:37:56,260 --> 00:37:57,770
being with him

829
00:37:57,860 --> 00:37:59,520
will really put you in danger.

830
00:38:00,980 --> 00:38:01,950
I'm going to bed.

831
00:38:01,970 --> 00:38:02,970
You should leave.

832
00:38:04,420 --> 00:38:05,170
Song Yiting!

833
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:07,460
You'll die!

834
00:38:12,170 --> 00:38:12,980
Guihong!

835
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:15,740
Guihong!

836
00:38:16,120 --> 00:38:16,930
Guihong.

837
00:38:17,260 --> 00:38:17,790
Guihong.

838
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:19,300
Something terrible has happened.

839
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,490
It's a disaster!

840
00:38:20,740 --> 00:38:21,690
Your Highness, please calm down.

841
00:38:21,690 --> 00:38:22,090
Take your time and tell me slowly.

842
00:38:22,090 --> 00:38:22,780
Listen,

843
00:38:23,210 --> 00:38:23,980
yesterday, I saw

844
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:25,130
Yiting and Li Shiliu

845
00:38:25,130 --> 00:38:26,090
together,

846
00:38:26,090 --> 00:38:28,010
and they seemed quite close.

847
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:28,820
So I immediately

848
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:30,090
had someone investigate

849
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:31,610
this mysterious Li Shiliu.

850
00:38:31,610 --> 00:38:33,260
I've already investigated him.

851
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:33,980
His background is clean,

852
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:34,980
with nothing suspicious.

853
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:35,420
Yes,

854
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,940
that's what I just found out.

855
00:38:36,940 --> 00:38:38,050
But I wasn't convinced,

856
00:38:38,050 --> 00:38:40,050
so I looked into the people around him,

857
00:38:40,050 --> 00:38:41,310
and guess what I found?

858
00:38:43,570 --> 00:38:44,380
He...

859
00:38:46,090 --> 00:38:46,900
Come here.

860
00:38:47,170 --> 00:38:47,650
Listen,

861
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:51,790
there's someone called Shangguan He
with him,

862
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:54,820
who's a death-row prisoner that
escaped from prison!

863
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:13,030
Search thoroughly!

864
00:39:13,050 --> 00:39:13,740
Yes!

865
00:39:14,150 --> 00:39:14,960
Search!

866
00:39:14,980 --> 00:39:15,690
Yes!

867
00:39:16,170 --> 00:39:17,220
Who dares!

868
00:39:41,090 --> 00:39:42,530
General Chu, you're certainly

869
00:39:42,530 --> 00:39:44,130
in a fiery mood this morning.

870
00:39:45,170 --> 00:39:47,370
Bringing the Qianyu Army here with you,

871
00:39:47,530 --> 00:39:49,060
what are you planning to do?

872
00:39:50,490 --> 00:39:53,260
I'm not here to trouble you today,

873
00:39:56,010 --> 00:39:57,530
but for him.

874
00:39:59,790 --> 00:40:01,020
May I ask, Mr. Chu,

875
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,900
what business do you have with me?

876
00:40:03,940 --> 00:40:05,310
Three years ago,

877
00:40:05,420 --> 00:40:06,680
in Jiangnan Province,

878
00:40:07,020 --> 00:40:08,230
Mr. Shangguan

879
00:40:08,470 --> 00:40:09,980
was accused of a serious crime

880
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:11,640
and faked his death to escape.

881
00:40:12,270 --> 00:40:13,810
Do I need to say more?

882
00:40:15,230 --> 00:40:16,020
Rong Hua.

883
00:40:16,610 --> 00:40:17,420
Wait!

884
00:40:18,490 --> 00:40:22,170
Though we at Waning River Crescent are
just nobodies from the martial arts world,

885
00:40:22,170 --> 00:40:24,010
you can't just take someone away

886
00:40:24,010 --> 00:40:25,260
with a few words.

887
00:40:25,570 --> 00:40:26,380
Li Shiliu.

888
00:40:27,090 --> 00:40:28,530
I'm here on official business on behalf of
the capital prefecture's office.

889
00:40:28,530 --> 00:40:30,050
How dare you obstruct me?

890
00:40:30,050 --> 00:40:32,780
So what if it's the
capital prefecture's office?

891
00:40:33,290 --> 00:40:34,770
Unless I give the word,

892
00:40:35,610 --> 00:40:37,010
you're not taking anyone away.

893
00:40:37,010 --> 00:40:39,300
What if I insist on taking him away?

894
00:40:45,610 --> 00:40:47,490
You're welcome to try.

895
00:40:50,110 --> 00:40:51,620
[Big Fortune]

